// Title: Local Administrator Group Discovery
// Description: Detects enumeration of local admin groups via SecurityEvent logs.
// Data Source: SecurityEvent
// MITRE ATT&CK:
//   Tactic: TA0007 - Discovery
//   Technique: T1087.002 - Local Group Discovery
// Severity: Medium

SecurityEvent
| where EventID == 4735 or EventID == 4737
| project TimeGenerated, Account, Computer, Activity
| order by TimeGenerated desc